# [How to Build a Tool-using ReAct Agent with Claude 3.5 and Python](#)

## We present a Reason+Act agent that iteratively reasons and gathers information from external tools before providing an answer.


This folder contains the code and data to support the article above.


_Files_

- `ct.ipynb` is the main notebook for this article - it implements the code and contains various examples of use
- ``c1.ipynb`` is a simple call to the Claude 3.5 LLM

